{"tid":391126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭大讚警務處「最佳公眾形象獎」銀獎實至名歸","createTime":"2017-09-07T14:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T15:57:27.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13acb9ddf259b4157d34813b90a5b071e4f573f8","tid":391126,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭大讚警務處「最佳公眾形象獎」銀獎實至名歸</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170907/s00001/9d085674e37efd4fbb57a298aba0b498.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170907%2Fs00001%2F9d085674e37efd4fbb57a298aba0b498.jpg&h=e08c8fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥今日主持公務員優質服務頒獎禮，她致辭時讚揚消防處、渠務署及警務處，又指警務處多年來得到「最佳公眾形象獎」銀獎，不怕抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，渠務署的跑馬地蓄洪池工程比預期早了一年完成，而且沒有超支；消防處在風暴期間，救出飛鵝山兩名內地行山人士，及後在網上看到一封公開信，表揚消防員危難之際仍能表現卓越，令她非常感動。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，警務處今年獲得「最佳公眾形象獎」銀獎「實在是實至名歸」，又指在2011、2013、2015及今日2017年，「警務處都係最佳公眾形象獎銀獎得主，換句話說，警務處係唔怕人抹黑，我哋為警務處鼓掌。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170907/s00001/1504790601170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170907%2Fs00001%2F1504790601170&d=Oob3F8YH%2FrSR4mjBHCHhgJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=ee2fec80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170907%2Fs00001%2F1504790601170&h=bd76cf80\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170907/s00001/1504790601170</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死黑警"},{"pid":"12f062013651482036831042b9794a0eba315f93","tid":391126,"uid":20448,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"本身都黑到反光 怕咩抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\